{"id":5275,"date":"2025-02-24T13:44:44","date_gmt":"2025-02-24T13:44:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/?page_id=5275"},"modified":"2025-11-11T19:36:24","modified_gmt":"2025-11-11T19:36:24","slug":"faqs","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/faqs\/","title":{"rendered":"FAQ&#8217;s"},"content":{"rendered":"<!-- title-bar-alt --><section class=\"section title-bar title-bar-fluid title-bar-dark inverted compact \">\n  <div\n    class=\"container relative z-20 flex items-center pointer-events-none\">\n    <div class=\"row w-full \">\n      <div class=\"w-full sm:w-11\/12\">\n                  <h1 class=\" mb-6\">FAQs<\/h1>\n                          <div class=\"content wysiwyg\">\n            <p>Your questions, answered.<\/p>\n          <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n    <div class=\"bg\">\n    <canvas class=\"webgl\"><\/canvas>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"gradient\">\n    <canvas id=\"hero-gradient\"><\/canvas>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- faq -->    \n<section class=\"section faqs overflow-hidden\">\n\n  <div class=\"container relative\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-between\">\n      <!-- Heading -->\n      <div class=\"w-full sm:w-1\/3\">\n                          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions<\/h2>\n                      <\/div>\n\n      <!-- FAQ -->\n              <!-- Mark this block as an FAQPage -->\n        <div class=\"w-full sm:w-3\/5\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/FAQPage\">\n          <dl class=\"accordion lg:mt-12\" data-chris >\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How long does it take to build a website?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>A simple brochure-style website might take 6-8 weeks, while a more complex site like an eCommerce store could take 12 weeks or more. The time frame depends on size, complexity, required features, and whether branding is needed. We can also work in an agile way or launch in phases for tighter timelines.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What is the cost of a web design project?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Our pricing depends on your requirements, with flexible staged payments. Projects typically range from \u00a310k ($12.5k) to \u00a3120k ($157k), with an average of around \u00a315-20k ($20k-26k). We have a minimum project size of \u00a310k ($12.5k).<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Will I retain full ownership of the design, development, and code?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Yes. Once the project is complete and paid in full, all design files and site assets are handed over and ownership is assigned to you. We do not retain ownership or lock you into ongoing fees.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What is the process for feedback, revisions, and approvals?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Our projects run in phases, with clear milestones for review and sign-off. We use tools like Figma for design and BugHerd for QA so you can comment directly on designs and pages. This iterative approach gives you structured opportunities to refine everything before final approval.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What ongoing support or maintenance do you offer after launch?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>We offer care plans, retainers, and ad hoc support so you can choose the level of help you need. A website is never really finished, and we are available to support future updates and improvements.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Will the website be mobile-friendly and responsive?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Yes. We design mobile views from the start and ensure the site works and looks right across mobiles, tablets, and desktops.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Can I easily update the content myself?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Yes. We build on industry-standard CMS platforms and structure content so you can create and edit pages quickly without needing a developer.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Will my website be optimised for search engines?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Yes. Our SEO team is involved in projects to ensure solid technical and on-page foundations from day one. We also provide ongoing SEO services if you want to push performance further.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Do I need branding for my website project?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Without clear brand foundations and assets, website and marketing designs often become inconsistent. We recommend creating or refining your brand identity and guidelines before or alongside your website project.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How long does a branding process take?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Allow around 1 week for discovery, 1-2 weeks for initial concepts, and up to 2 weeks for visual identity and brand guidelines. Most branding projects take 4-6 weeks depending on complexity and feedback.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">I have a logo already. Is this enough?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>A logo is a strong start, but not a full brand. To design an effective, consistent website you will also need a defined colour palette, typography, imagery, and supporting assets.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Why is branding important for my business?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Branding shapes how people recognise, understand, and trust your business. It guides your messaging, visuals, and experience across your website, social channels, and marketing, helping you stand out and build loyalty.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What are brand guidelines, and do I need them?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Brand guidelines set out how your logo, colours, typography, imagery, and assets should be used. They keep everything consistent, especially when multiple people or teams create content. We strongly recommend having guidelines in place before major design work.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What does digital marketing encompass?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Digital marketing covers channels such as SEO, PPC, content, social media, and email used together to increase visibility, traffic, and conversions.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How do you measure the success of a digital marketing campaign?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>We track KPIs like traffic growth, search visibility, engagement, conversion rates, and leads or revenue generated, aligned to your goals.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What kind of businesses do you work with?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>We work with start ups, SMEs, and established brands across a wide range of sectors in the UK and internationally.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How do you create a digital marketing strategy for my business?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>We review your goals, audience, data, and competitors, then design a channel mix across SEO, content, PPC, and social that fits your objectives and budget.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How long will it take to see results from a digital marketing campaign?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>PPC can generate results quickly. Sustainable organic growth from SEO and content usually takes several months. We set expectations at the outset based on your situation.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How long does the website audit take?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>A typical website audit takes around 2 weeks. As it is manually completed by our team, timings can vary slightly based on scope and workload. We confirm a clear timeframe when you book.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Will you fix the problems you find during the audit?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>The audit highlights issues and opportunities. Fixes are not included by default, but we can quote to implement them and often provide discounted rates for audit clients.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Is it a manual review or automated?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>It is a fully manual review by our team. We may use tools for data, but your recommendations are based on human analysis, not a generic automated report.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Do you look at my website&#8217;s SEO performance as part of the audit?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Yes. We review traffic, rankings, on site optimisation, technical health, and highlight SEO opportunities.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How do you ensure my website stays secure?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>We use SSL, hardened hosting, regular updates, firewalls, malware scanning, and frequent backups to help protect your site.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Will I have control over my hosting account?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Yes. You have full access to your hosting account. We also provide management support if you would like us to handle it for you.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How often do you back up websites?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>We take daily backups so your site can be restored quickly if needed.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What happens if my website goes down?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Our monitoring alerts us if your site is unavailable and we work to resolve issues quickly while keeping you informed.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What is the difference between regular hosting and WordPress hosting?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>WordPress hosting is tuned specifically for WordPress sites, typically offering faster performance, added security, and tools that support updates and management.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How accurate is the SEO Checker?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>It provides a reliable view of common SEO issues using proven metrics. No automated tool covers every nuance, so for deeper insight we recommend a manual review from our SEO team.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">I need help with the results from my SEO Checker.<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\